highlights.text: “Maledetta primavera” by Loretta Goggi is the highest new entry on Top Songs Italy at #129.
“Destri” by Gazzelle has been on Top Songs Italy the longest, at 952 days straight.
Sfera Ebbasta has the most spots on Top Songs Italy. “Yakuza” is the highest at #6.
“Can't Hold Us (feat. Ray Dalton)” by Macklemore, Ryan Lewis, Macklemore & Ryan Lewis, and Ray Dalton is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Italy, up 46 spots at #151.
